592450</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2)文宣Post</span></strong></span><br />\n[國恨家仇] 黑警發鼠瘟暴行GIF集合 612-925<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592752</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3)聲援手足Post</span></strong></span><br />\n法庭要人聲援！聽日46位手足上庭！43個暴動、1個冇得保釋坐緊啦！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後，善用不推文！"},{"pid":"91268261959ed90900d95b0ee1fb8f389cacd3c5","tid":1592742,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ba52652301d26aae3eaa153dbafde5789de9b5","tid":1592742,"uid":282328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T18:18:05.000Z","msg":"幫幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />p牌無撚用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T18:49:43.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但開post前可以睇下出面係咪有相關嘅post<br />\n專心推幾個<br />\n好過係咁開新post"},{"pid":"1db89d1a2d9e5a937e754c5cb2eaf5c8dec3a901","tid":1592742,"uid":282328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91268261959ed90900d95b0ee1fb8f389cacd3c5","tid":1592742,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ba52652301d26aae3eaa153dbafde5789de9b5","tid":1592742,"uid":282328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T18:18:05.000Z","msg":"幫幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />p牌無撚用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T18:49:43.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但開post前可以睇下出面係咪有相關嘅post<br />\n專心推幾個<br />\n好過係咁開新post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T18:55:36.000Z","msg":"我見無最updated 同埋無整合左連文宣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" c